name: "Taco Pixies Gang Gang!" - a tribute to Tacopixies.tez
description:
My contribution to the #tacos4tacopixies challenge by @tacopixies by @mumu_thestan
Mumu's Taco Pixies project has been a huge influence and inspired me to start my Galactibles.xyz. Give them a follow and collect their Taco Pixies at tacopixies.tez! 41 frames, 46 layers, made with Aseprite.
